1.0: LCARS Lights Control - Initial Release
* Complete rewrite of original LCARS clock for smart home control
* BATTERY SAFETY: Aggressive power optimization with smart polling
* Home Assistant integration with REST API and Bearer token auth
* Control up to 6 lights with on/off status and brightness display
* Music control screen with Gadgetbridge integration (Spotify, etc.)
* Three screens: Clock, Light Control, Music Control
* Navigation via left/right swipe between screens
* Touch controls: tap lights to toggle, tap music controls
* LCARS authentic design with rounded end caps and themed colors
* Configurable polling intervals (30-300 seconds, default: 120s)
* Automatic offline mode after connection failures
* Screen-aware polling (only when light screen active and LCD on)
* Efficient display updates with caching to prevent unnecessary redraws
* Comprehensive settings interface with Home Assistant configuration
* Quick setup examples and detailed battery optimization tips
* Error handling with exponential backoff and connection reset
* Proper cleanup of all intervals and timers on app exit
* Support for both local and cloud Home Assistant instances
* Weather display from Gadgetbridge (temperature, humidity)
* Battery indicator with visual progress bar
* Random planet images (Earth, Mars, Moon, Saturn)
* Fullscreen mode support with widget hiding
* 35+ configurable color themes plus random color mode
* Complete documentation with setup guide and troubleshooting
* Expected battery life: 24+ hours with normal usage
* HTTP/HTTPS support for secure HA connections
* Entity ID validation and smart parsing
* Connection status indicators (ONLINE/OFFLINE)
* Manual connection retry by tapping offline status
* Music progress tracking with time display
* Artist, track, album information display
* Play/pause, next/previous track controls
* Compatible with any music app supporting Gadgetbridge
* Light entity support for standard Home Assistant light entities
* Real-time brightness levels shown as LCARS progress bars
* Touch zones for intuitive light and music control
* Settings include battery tips and Home Assistant setup help
* Maintains original LCARS planet rotation and visual elements
* Memory-efficient implementation with minimal allocations
* Network timeout protection (5 second max per request)
* Smart failure detection stops polling after 3 consecutive failures
* Zero network activity when screen off or on non-HA screens
* Display caching prevents redundant screen updates
* Proper font cleanup and event listener removal
* Compatible with Bangle.js 2 (176x176 screen)
* Based on original LCARS app but completely rewritten for smart home use

ORIGINAL LCARS CLOCK HISTORY:
0.01-0.32: Original LCARS clock development by David Peer and contributors
* Features included: alarms, health tracking, weather, theming
* See original LCARS app for detailed version history